@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About Senior Health Partners";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<main aria-labelledby="title">
    <h1 id="title">@ViewBag.Title</h1>

    <p>Welcome to <strong>Senior Health Partners</strong>, a dedicated platform aiming to enhance the quality of healthcare services provided to the elderly. Our services are designed to ensure easy access and efficient management of healthcare information for doctors, patients, and administrators.</p>

    <h3>Services Overview</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>
            <strong>Doctor Rating System:</strong>
            Patients can rate doctors based on their experience, helping to maintain a high standard of service and providing feedback for continuous improvement.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Medication Management:</strong>
            Doctors can prescribe medications to their patients, view their medication history, and manage dosages to ensure accurate treatment.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Patient Medication Management:</strong>
            Patients can view their current and past medications, track dosages, and receive notifications for medication times to improve adherence.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Doctor Information Management:</strong>
            Doctors can update their professional information, making it easier for patients to find and contact them based on their specialties and availability.
        </li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Future Developments</h3>
    <p>Looking ahead, <strong>Senior Health Partners</strong> plans to introduce several advanced features:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>
            <strong>Medical Email Reminders:</strong>
            An automated system that will send email reminders to patients for their medication schedules and upcoming appointments.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Geolocation Services:</strong>
            Integration of mapping services to help patients locate medical facilities and doctors' offices quickly and efficiently.
        </li>
    </ul>

    <p>Our goal is to provide a seamless and supportive environment for all elderly care needs, facilitating better health management and accessibility.</p>
</main>
